{"tid":110263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨胡志偉：23條立法若做好諮詢較大機會達共識","createTime":"2017-02-06T14:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T17:38:31.000Z","uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8053a1a29420f1ecd2252946e179043ec4376693","tid":110263,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"特首參選人曾俊華今日發表政綱，表明將盡力推行《基本法》第23條立法。民主黨主席胡志偉回應稱，政府若有充分諮詢，社會有較大機會就23條達成共識。他又認為23條若以寬鬆方法推行，不令市民覺得出現以言入罪，影響言論自由、新聞自由的話，將不會引起公眾恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉今日就23條立法表達立場，稱政府若經充分諮詢有機會達成共識，「如果你能吸納教訓，做好應有的諮詢過程，令整個立法不會令香港市民擔心以言入罪的事情。通過立法過程會做得到的話，我覺得尋找到共識的機會大很多」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指23條立法若寬鬆處理，不致於引起公眾恐慌，「如果能夠找到路徑處理這政治制度的問題，23條立法若用比較寬鬆的處理，不會令市民覺得出現以言入罪，影響言論自由、新聞自由的話，我覺得這問題其實不會令公眾引起恐慌」。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉稱，民主黨暫時未有提名決定，會與所有參選人會面後再詳細討論。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華的政綱提及，特區按《基本法》第23條規定，自行立法維護國家安全，「是必須履行的憲制責任」，並指「我認為，問題不在於要否為第 23 條立法， 而在於法例的具體內容和範圍，以及立法的正當程序」，表明會汲取2002、2003年立法不成功的經驗，「盡力推行23條立法，完成一項維護香港和國家安全，並為港人接受的法例」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89-23%E6%A2%9D%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E8%8B%A5%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2-%E8%BC%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E9%81%94%E5%85%B1%E8%AD%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589-23%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%25AB%25AE%25E8%25A9%25A2-%25E8%25BC%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%2594%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%25AD%2598%2F&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2f8bd0da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589-23%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%25AB%25AE%25E8%25A9%25A2-%25E8%25BC%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%2594%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%25AD%2598%2F&h=f1fdcce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89-23%E6%A2%9D%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E8%8B%A5%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2-%E8%BC%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E9%81%94%E5%85%B1%E8%AD%98/</a>"},{"pid":"2aafe7c81274e1332ffdc19c5f58f2cb38cf40c3","tid":110263,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"呢班賤人到底仲想點"},{"pid":"37c9d85c23abf1a5dab46bea1450ff6a57fa4fbd","tid":110263,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"變色龍"},{"pid":"c9a321a8fbb113e750d3914f8561b005d92d16aa","tid":110263,"uid":43116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"},{"pid":"3171193720037a3d93910dd32462aea518f13c2b","tid":110263,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:38:17.000Z","msg":"民主黨完全演譯今天的我打倒昨日的我<br />\n<br />\n正式宣佈加入民建議b隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc616f0b670a5516afb8982895cacf364d749dce","tid":110263,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"含淚投民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0bd66f6070e5127caed5a71d7190929067e1b8","tid":110263,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"正賤種"},{"pid":"b0474930d516b3377193770cf57392c935264dcd","tid":110263,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:11:56.000Z","msg":"呢d遲早變馮偉肛"},{"pid":"97453becf94f454f4a293e88e784e8fd85508b4c","tid":110263,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:19:10.000Z","msg":"我要廿三條立法咁投民主黨把撚啊？"},{"pid":"cdeaca56fd54a0988d2d41e7d1c86c5aba44d927","tid":110263,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal